"""Deterministic migration of source skills into Codex artifacts.

This is the skill-owned implementation behind the stable root wrapper:
`scripts/migrate_claude_workflows_to_codex.py`.

Behavioral contract:
  - `--skill <name>` migrates a single source skill
  - `--all` migrates every non-archived source skill
  - zero-argument invocation behaves as `--all`
  - `--dry-run` computes work without writing files
"""

